{"content": "<h2>The Artist: Jubbish aka Jay</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Jubbish (aka jay) is a lens based artist who thrives in the paradoxical space between chaos and precision. His work seems like a riff on the absurd, flipping the banal into visual puns and abstract commentary that feels oddly resonant with internet-native culture. He’s got a knack for making the deeply surreal feel approachable, balancing a lo-fi aesthetic with high-concept undertones. Afaict... dude’s playing 4D chess with vibes rn, pulling from memetics, pop detritus, and glitchy existential dread. His art feels like a visual shitpost with the emotional weight of camus yelling into a void. Follow him or don't, but either way, he’s out here doing something weirdly meaningful.</p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"999\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jubbish-profile-768x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jubbish-profile-768x1023.jpg 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jubbish-profile-225x300.jpg 225w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jubbish-profile-1153x1536.jpg 1153w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jubbish-profile-400x533.jpg 400w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jubbish-profile-1320x1759.jpg 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jubbish-profile-600x800.jpg 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Jubbish-profile.jpg 1500w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Jay aka Jubbish</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>The Collection: Jubbish</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>Inspired by renaissance paintings... Jubbish is what peak performance looks like in atmospheric light manipulation. You can't fake the surreal..nor can you paint with a lens... or can you? In any event, game recognizes game with camera whisperers Brendan North, Brynn Alise, Dave Krugman, Ben Skaar and Matt Doogue all taking up a position in the tokenized life of <a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf/explore/ETHEREUM:0xb216c511bd9029baf1f2c3000f46ee941ca3ea04?sort=cheapest\">Jubbish.</a></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figure>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf/explore/ETHEREUM:0xb216c511bd9029baf1f2c3000f46ee941ca3ea04?sort=cheapest\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"522\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jubbish-collection-1024x714.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jubbish-collection-1024x714.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jubbish-collection-300x209.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jubbish-collection-768x535.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jubbish-collection-1536x1071.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jubbish-collection-2048x1427.png 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jubbish-collection-1320x920.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/jubbish-collection-600x418.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<figcaption>Jubbish collection</figcaption>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t</figure>\n\t\t\t<h2>A Specific Artwork: My Sun and Moon</h2>\t\t\n\t\t<p>The daily patterns of life metaphorically summed up through a refractive index informed view across red rock country in Utah. Our entire lives summed up in two rocks...and the journey we make between them. <a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf/token/ETHEREUM:0xb216c511bd9029baf1f2c3000f46ee941ca3ea04:18\">'My Sun and Moon' is now listed for 1.5 eth in The Line Gift Shop.</a></p>\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"499\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/my-sun-and-moon-1024x682.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/my-sun-and-moon-1024x682.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/my-sun-and-moon-300x200.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/my-sun-and-moon-768x511.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/my-sun-and-moon-1536x1022.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/my-sun-and-moon-1320x879.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/my-sun-and-moon-600x399.png 600w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/my-sun-and-moon.png 1782w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<blockquote>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\"Sun on the left in light, Moon on the right in shadow. Watching the clouds drift overhead like lazy whales in an inverted sea, casting shadows on the ocean floor.\"\t\t\t</p>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<cite>Jubbish</cite>\n\t\t\t\t\t</blockquote>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<img width=\"749\" height=\"450\" src=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-14-at-9.22.38 AM-1024x615.png\" alt=\"\" srcset=\"https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-14-at-9.22.38 AM-1024x615.png 1024w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-14-at-9.22.38 AM-300x180.png 300w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-14-at-9.22.38 AM-768x461.png 768w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-14-at-9.22.38 AM-1536x923.png 1536w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-14-at-9.22.38 AM-2048x1230.png 2048w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-14-at-9.22.38 AM-1320x793.png 1320w, https://pub-40df8e6473b14a10a093ecf8c80c2f92.r2.dev/migrated/wp-content/uploads/2025/01/Screenshot-2025-01-14-at-9.22.38 AM-600x360.png 600w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 749px) 100vw, 749px\" />\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://theline.wtf/listing/jubbish-aka-jay/\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tJubbish | Line 806\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>\n\t\t\t\t\t<a href=\"https://giftshop.theline.wtf/token/ETHEREUM:0xb216c511bd9029baf1f2c3000f46ee941ca3ea04:18\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tExit via The Line Gift Shop\n\t\t\t\t\t</a>"}